name: rover_segmentation_using_kmeans
description: The project is designed to segment an image into rover, background, and shadows using a stepwise image processing algorithms. This includes color space conversion, blurring, normalization, optional contrast enhancement, feature reshaping, k-means clustering, mask merging, and morphological refinement.
